        GarakRemoteEvalAdapter -->|extends| GarakEvalBase
        GarakInlineEvalAdapter -->|extends| GarakEvalBase
        GarakEvalBase -->|uses| GarakCommandConfig
        GarakEvalBase -->|uses| GarakScanConfig
        GarakRemoteEvalAdapter -->|submits| KFPPipeline
        GarakInlineEvalAdapter -->|runs locally| GarakScan
        GarakScan -->|orchestrates| SimpleShieldOrchestrator
    end

