    GarakRemoteEvalAdapter -->|HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token| DSPA["DSPA / KFP API"]
    GarakScan -->|HTTPS/443<br/>API Key| vLLM["vLLM Model Server"]
    ParseResults -->|HTTP/8321| FilesAPI["Llama Stack Files API"]
    SimpleShieldOrchestrator -->|HTTP/8321| SafetyAPI["Llama Stack Safety API"]
    LlamaStackServer -->|TCP/5432| PostgreSQL["PostgreSQL"]
    EvalHubAdapter -->|HTTPS/443| S3["S3 / MinIO"]

