    TrustyAIOp["TrustyAI Service Operator<br/>ConfigMap"] -.->|garak-provider-image| GarakRemoteEvalAdapter
    LSOp["Llama Stack Operator<br/>LlamaStackDistribution CR"] -.->|manages| LlamaStackDist

